trans-unit.source: Represents the compiler settings used within the ASP.NET build environment to generate and compile source code from a virtual path.
trans-unit.target: Representa as configurações de compilador usadas no ambiente de compilação do ASP.NET para gerar e compilar o código-fonte de um caminho virtual.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.CodeCompilerType%2A> property of a <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider> implementation to examine the settings used to generate and compile source code from a virtual path for that build provider.
trans-unit.target: Use o <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.CodeCompilerType%2A>propriedade de um <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider>implementação para examinar as configurações usadas para gerar e compilar o código-fonte de um caminho virtual para o provedor de compilação.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.CodeCompilerType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The ASP.NET build environment uses <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider> objects to generate source code for custom file types within the project.
trans-unit.target: O ASP.NET usa do ambiente de compilação <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider>objetos para gerar o código-fonte para os tipos de arquivos personalizados dentro do projeto.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider>

trans-unit.source: Classes derived from <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider> provide build details for source files, Web pages, resources, and other custom items.
trans-unit.target: Classes derivadas de <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider>fornecer detalhes de compilação para arquivos de origem, páginas da Web, recursos e outros itens personalizados.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider>

trans-unit.source: When the build provider requires a specific programming language, it overrides the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.CodeCompilerType%2A> property and calls the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.GetDefaultCompilerType%2A> method to return a CompilerType object for the supported programming language.
trans-unit.target: Quando o provedor de compilação requer uma linguagem de programação específica, ele substitui o <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.CodeCompilerType%2A>propriedade e chama o <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.GetDefaultCompilerType%2A>método para retornar um objeto CompilerType para a linguagem de programação com suporte.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.GetDefaultCompilerType%2A> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.CodeCompilerType%2A>

trans-unit.source: To set the CompilerType object within a build provider implementation, use the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.GetDefaultCompilerType%2A> method or the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.GetDefaultCompilerTypeForLanguage%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Para definir o objeto CompilerType dentro de uma implementação de provedor de compilação, use o <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.GetDefaultCompilerType%2A>método ou o <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.GetDefaultCompilerTypeForLanguage%2A>método.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.GetDefaultCompilerTypeForLanguage%2A> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider.GetDefaultCompilerType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType.CodeDomProviderType%2A> property specifies the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider> implementation used to generate and compile source code for a build provider.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType.CodeDomProviderType%2A>propriedade especifica o <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>implementação usada para gerar e compilar o código-fonte para um provedor de compilação.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType.CodeDomProviderType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType.CompilerParameters%2A> property defines the settings used to compile the source code into an assembly.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType.CompilerParameters%2A>propriedade define as configurações usadas para compilar o código-fonte em um assembly.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType.CompilerParameters%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref:System.Type> for the configured <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider"></xref> implementation.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um <xref:System.Type>configurado <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider"> </xref> implementação.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The CodeDomProviderType property specifies the <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider> implementation used to generate and compile source code for a build provider.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade CodeDomProviderType Especifica o <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>implementação usada para gerar e compilar o código-fonte para um provedor de compilação.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CodeDomProvider>

trans-unit.source: For example, if the build provider is configured to use the Visual Basic code provider in the .NET Framework, CodeDomProviderType returns a <xref:System.Type> for the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.VBCodeProvider> class.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, se o provedor de compilação está configurado para usar o provedor de código do Visual Basic no .NET Framework, CodeDomProviderType retorna um <xref:System.Type>para a <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.VBCodeProvider>classe.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.VBCodeProvider> </xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: A read-only <xref:System.Type> that represents the configured code provider type.
trans-unit.target: Somente leitura <xref:System.Type>que representa o tipo de provedor de código configurado.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Gets the settings and options used to compile source code into an assembly.
trans-unit.target: Obtém as configurações e opções usadas para compilar o código-fonte em um assembly.

trans-unit.source: Use the CompilerParameters property to examine the compiler options configured for the compiler.
trans-unit.target: Use a propriedade CompilerParameters para examinar as opções de compilador configuradas para o compilador.

trans-unit.source: The CompilerParameters property specifies whether warnings are treated as errors, whether the compiler output includes debug information, and other compiler settings.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade CompilerParameters Especifica se os avisos são tratados como erros, se a saída do compilador inclui informações de depuração e outras configurações de compilador.

trans-unit.source: A read-only <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters"></xref> object that represents the settings and options of the code compiler.
trans-unit.target: Somente leitura <xref href="System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters"> </xref> objeto que representa as configurações e opções do compilador de código.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified object represents the same code provider and compiler settings as the current instance of <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Determina se o objeto especificado representa os mesmo código compilador e o provedor de configurações como a instância atual do <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The Equals method overrides the <xref:System.Object.Equals%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: O método Equals substitui o <xref:System.Object.Equals%2A?displayProperty=fullName>método.</xref:System.Object.Equals%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Equals compares two instances based on their <xref:System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType.CodeDomProviderType%2A>, <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.WarningLevel%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.CompilerOptions%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, and <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.IncludeDebugInformation%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties.
trans-unit.target: Equals Compara duas instâncias com base em seus <xref:System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType.CodeDomProviderType%2A>, <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.WarningLevel%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.CompilerOptions%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, e <xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.IncludeDebugInformation%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Propriedades.</xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.IncludeDebugInformation%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.CompilerOptions%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.CodeDom.Compiler.CompilerParameters.WarningLevel%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType.CodeDomProviderType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The object to compare with the current instance of <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: O objeto a ser comparado com a instância atual do <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: if o is a object and its value is the same as this instance; otherwise, .
trans-unit.target: Se o é um objeto e seu valor é o mesmo que esta instância; caso contrário, .

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code for this instance.
trans-unit.target: Retorna o código hash para essa instância.

trans-unit.source: The GetHashCode method overrides the <xref:System.Object.GetHashCode%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: O método GetHashCode substitui o <xref:System.Object.GetHashCode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>método.</xref:System.Object.GetHashCode%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: GetHashCode generates the same hash code for two objects that are equal according to the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType.Equals%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: GetHashCode gera o mesmo código de hash de dois objetos são iguais de acordo com o <xref:System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType.Equals%2A>método.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType.Equals%2A>

trans-unit.source: A 32-bit signed integer hash code for the current instance of <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType"></xref>, suitable for use in hashing algorithms and data structures, such as a hash table.
trans-unit.target: Um código de hash de inteiro de 32 bits para a instância atual do <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.CompilerType"> </xref>, adequado para uso em algoritmos e estruturas de dados, como uma tabela de hash de hash.
